metadata.description: Historical Figures builds upon Rewind Collectiveâ€™s commitment of championing women & the underrepresented. Series 4 of these digital artworks consists of five female figures throughout history, fictional and real, who are warriors, leaders, & revolutionaries. Their lives or their myths have inspired millions of people throughout the ages. The editioned works consist of glitched pixels, combining original photography and design to launch these series.
